name: Doomsday's Vault
description: This level is composed of several levels that I made for a cancelled 4 level wad. I didn't want all my time to go to waste, so I put them together and made this. .::STORY I MADE UP::. While your first victories were enough to put the Icon of Sin's minions and itself on their knees. The surviving forces are planning a secret attack on the starports to turn the returning survivors of their failed invasion into a new army of living dead. Luckily, you just happen to go through their hideout while making your way back.
